<bibRefCitation author="PORTIER B." box="[566,700,1919,1943]" pageId="12" pageNumber="37" pagination="139 - 140" refId="ref68379" refString="PORTIER B. 2002 a. - Red-necked Nightjar Caprimulgus ruficollis, new to Burkina Faso. Bulletin of the African Bird Club 9: 139 - 140." type="journal article" year="2002">Portier 2002a</bibRefCitation>
