<bibRefCitation author="BORROW N. &amp; DEMEY R." box="[251,503,1946,1970]" pageId="12" pageNumber="37" refId="ref65186" refString="BORROW N. &amp; DEMEY R. 2014. - Field Guide of the Birds of Western Africa. II edition. Christopher Helm, London, 592 p." type="book" year="2014">Borrow &amp; Demey (2014)</bibRefCitation>
